			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A\r\n- Go to the Tombstone shop door (goto 68 41 21) (near S_LOW_MurderTribunal_TombstoneShop_Door_ef23ee25-c62e-4fab-badd-4f98e364ebd5)\r\n- Use \"oe MT_Start\" to go to the door OR\r\nuse \"oe MT_GetDolorItems\", read Orin's note and learn the Word of Passage that will open the door.\r\n- Interact with the door while it is still locked."
				},
